{"tid":503104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又係蝗！劏房碎屍女童 8歲時隨母獲批來港定居","createTime":"2017-12-18T13:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T14:45:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f07033289f2d828de51e03743df4d07dcac81d","tid":503104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T13:59:50.000Z","msg":"慘遭殺害的女童何美洁生於破碎家庭，自小已成為「人球」遭拋來拋去。據了解，美洁在<span style=\"color: red;\">四川出生，父母在她年幼時離婚，其後她隨母親生活，及後母親嫁到香港，她8歲時亦隨母獲批來港定居</span>。雖然與生父分隔兩地，但父女感情深厚，一直保持聯絡，生父曾特意來港探望，與愛女團聚。<br />\n<br />\n然而，早前其母因事不能照顧美洁，將美洁送返內地由生父照顧，直至約一年半前，美洁再被送返香港，與母親居於案發的劏房，並在附近的小學入讀4年級。雖然「漂流」於父母之間，更因此被迫停學及轉校，但她仍努力學習，操行及學業成績均表現優秀，今學年順利升讀6年級，原定來年考讀心儀中學。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方事發後從校方取得緊急聯絡人資料，透過美洁在港的親友，取得其四川生父的聯絡方法，現正設法與他聯絡，以了解美洁生前與母親相處的情況，以及他們的家庭背景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171218/bkn-20171218205143618-1218_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171218%2Fbkn-20171218205143618-1218_00822_001.html&d=uhb2jV%2FeVWKqnXQ%2FwAnWh10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7a868e57\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171218/bkn-20171218205143618-1218_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"95c74b87d2a58f9b11f537ebf358fa2781ed95c1","tid":503104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1048b8a6854d6451680e71df1387904254a3bb58","tid":503104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"whole family係蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji